#     2. clock             :      source clock driving the cell
#     3. clock_polarity    :      clock polarity of the cell rising edge(+) and falling edge(-)
#     4. type              :      scannability status of the cell
#     5. hier_name         :      hierarchical name of the cell
#     6. lib_cell_name     :      Library cell name of the cell
